original_title: Miss Edmonton Teenburger 1983 in: It's Party Time!
overview: Watch in awe as Miss Edmonton TeenBurger 1983 graces the screen in her first featurette, "IT'S PARTY TIME!". A story as layered as her hair, as ethereal as her style. A pop explosion of Ukranian delight that will leave you bedazzled. Are you ready?
title: Miss Edmonton Teenburger 1983 in: It's Party Time!
